$$x = \begin{pmatrix} I \\ \dot I \end{pmatrix}$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{d x}{d t} &amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \dot I \\ \ddot I \end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= \begin{pmatrix} \dot I \\ - \frac{R}{L} \dot I - \frac{1}{LC}I \end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= \begin{pmatrix} 
&amp;0 &amp;1 \\ 
&amp;-\frac{1}{LC} &amp;-\frac{R}{L} 
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix} I \\ \dot I \end{pmatrix} \\
&amp;= \begin{pmatrix} 
&amp;0 &amp;1 \\ 
&amp;-\frac{1}{LC} &amp;-\frac{R}{L} 
\end{pmatrix} x
\end{align*}
$$

&amp;0 &amp;1 \\ 
&amp;-\frac{1}{LC} &amp;-\frac{R}{L} 
\end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix} 
&amp;0 &amp;1 \\ 
&amp;-\frac{4}{R^2} &amp;-\frac{4}{R} 
\end{pmatrix}$$


$$|A - \lambda I | = 0$$

$$\Rightarrow (\lambda + \frac{2}{R})^2 = 0$$

故特征值为 $\lambda_1 = \lambda_2 = - \frac{2}{R}$

解得特征向量$a_0 = \begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}$

广义特征向量

$$(A - \lambda I) a_1 = a_0$$

$$a_1 = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ - \frac{R}{2} \end{pmatrix}$$

所以

$$x = c_1 e^{-\frac{2}{R}t}\begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix} + c_2 e^{-\frac{2}{R}t}\left(\begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}t + \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ - \frac{R}{2} div.data-content:
令

$$x = \begin{pmatrix} I \\ \dot I \end{pmatrix}$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{d x}{d t} &= \begin{pmatrix} \dot I \\ \ddot I \end{pmatrix} \\
&= \begin{pmatrix} \dot I \\ - \frac{R}{L} \dot I - \frac{1}{LC}I \end{pmatrix} \\
&= \begin{pmatrix}
&0 &1 \\
&-\frac{1}{LC} &-\frac{R}{L}
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix} I \\ \dot I \end{pmatrix} \\
&= \begin{pmatrix}
&0 &1 \\
&-\frac{1}{LC} &-\frac{R}{L}
\end{pmatrix} x
\end{align*}
$$

div.data-content:
$$A = \begin{pmatrix}
&0 &1 \\
&-\frac{1}{LC} &-\frac{R}{L}
\end{pmatrix} = \begin{pmatrix}
&0 &1 \\
&-\frac{4}{R^2} &-\frac{4}{R}
\end{pmatrix}$$


$$|A - \lambda I | = 0$$

$$\Rightarrow (\lambda + \frac{2}{R})^2 = 0$$

故特征值为 $\lambda_1 = \lambda_2 = - \frac{2}{R}$

解得特征向量$a_0 = \begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}$

广义特征向量

$$(A - \lambda I) a_1 = a_0$$

$$a_1 = \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ - \frac{R}{2} \end{pmatrix}$$

所以

$$x = c_1 e^{-\frac{2}{R}t}\begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix} + c_2 e^{-\frac{2}{R}t}\left(\begin{pmatrix} - \frac{R}{2} \\ 1 \end{pmatrix}t + \begin{pmatrix} 0 \\ - \frac{R}{2} \end{pmatrix} \right)$$
